## Verification

### DevTool Suite
1. Ensure the server is running: `node server.js`.
2. Send a message in the chat.
3. Refresh the page—your history will now persist reliably!
4. Check the model dropdown to see the new Gemini 2.0 and Flash Lite options.

### Video Directory
1. Open the [index.html](file:///c:/Users/shoaib/Documents/ai-video-models-directory/index.html) in your browser.
2. Scroll to the bottom of the models list or search for "Gemini" to see the new additions.
